<section class="section s5-process">
  <div class="container--narrow">

    <h2 class="s5-process__heading">Simple, Relaxing, and Effective</h2>

    <div class="s5-process__steps">

      <div class="s5-process__step">
        <div class="s5-process__step-num" aria-hidden="true">1</div>
        <div class="s5-process__step-body">
          <h3 class="s5-process__step-title">Personalized Consultation</h3>
          <p class="s5-process__step-desc">Your session begins with a brief consultation with one of our registered nurses. They will review your wellness goals and answer any questions to ensure your treatment is perfectly suited to your needs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="s5-process__step">
        <div class="s5-process__step-num" aria-hidden="true">2</div>
        <div class="s5-process__step-body">
          <h3 class="s5-process__step-title">Relax and Recharge</h3>
          <p class="s5-process__step-desc">Once settled in our comfortable therapy lounge, the IV drip is administered. The process is virtually painless and takes about 45-60 minutes. You can relax, read, or catch up on emails while your body absorbs the nutrients.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="s5-process__step">
        <div class="s5-process__step-num" aria-hidden="true">3</div>
        <div class="s5-process__step-body">
          <h3 class="s5-process__step-title">Feel the Benefits</h3>
          <p class="s5-process__step-desc">Many clients report an immediate feeling of revitalization, clarity, and overall well-being after their session. This foundational blend of nutrients will continue to support your system, helping you feel balanced, energized, and ready to take on your week.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .s5-process .container--narrow {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .s5-process__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .s5-process__steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .s5-process__step {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .s5-process__step-num {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-cta);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .s5-process__step-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    padding-top: 10px;
  }

  .s5-process__step-title {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: var(--weight-bold);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .s5-process__step-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
